==Awards==
*Played in the [[ECHL]] All-Star Game in [[2003<U+2013>04 ECHL season|2004]].
*Won the [[Most Exciting Player Award]] (Vancouver Canucks) in [[2007<U+2013>08 NHL season|2008]] and [[2008<U+2013>09 NHL season|2009]].
*Won the [[Fred J. Hume Award]] (Vancouver Canucks' unsung hero) in 2008.

